<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="blow-n">blow <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bləʊ/    美 /bloʊ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>重击；击打：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I killed two flies at one blow. 
我一下子打死了两只苍蝇。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>struck</strong> his enemy <strong>a</strong> heavy <strong>blow</strong> on the head. 
他在敌人头上重重一击。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(精神上的) 打击：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His wife’s death was a great <strong>blow to</strong> him. 
妻子的离世对他打击很大。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>吹：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try to put the candles out in one blow. 
用力一口气把蜡烛都吹灭。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The failure was a big blow <strong><em>_</em></strong> him, but he wasn’t discouraged and soon got as enthusiastic as ever.   （2015 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. to  </p></div>